{"tid":2273134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據了解港台管理層稱蔡玉玲非公務員　難提供法律支援","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T23:19:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d42076bb0a670439ebefe433a377b6ee88f35d8a","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"香港電台管理層下午就編導蔡玉玲被捕事件，與部分員工會面。據了解，副廣播處長馮建業在會上解釋，根據公務員事務規例，只有公務員獲得法律支援，但蔡玉玲屬「服務提供者」的合約形式聘用，並非公務員，難以提供法律支援，管方會向相關部門了解，港台是否可以豁免，但難以保證能否在蔡玉玲下周二提堂前獲具體回覆。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，廣播處長梁家榮在會上表示，港台屬政府部門，受到公務員事務規例約束，面對很多不同關卡，但強調蔡玉玲屬港台員工，為港台服務，會盡可能提供一切可行協助。消息指，他個人亦擔心，如果其他有份製作該節目的員工也被指犯法，應如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，會上亦有員工關注，如果警方突然到港台電視部搜證，當時沒有律政司的代表在場，可否自行尋求律師到場。管方回應，港台的法律代表是律政司，理論上是不可以。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">消息又指，會上有人關注會否將被指涉事的《鏗鏘集：7.21誰主真相》抽起，梁家榮回應，想不到有任何理由需要抽起，強調該報道並非有錯，只是報道事實，反問是否因為驚而抽起。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558561-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558561-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8nljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=0f910b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558561-20201105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=66146e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558561-20201105.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"56dfd49b21dbd853b2d631bf9ab105b3e7b05dd8","tid":2273134,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c159761190d0b02b6bd40a00ba432b8095cbcabb","tid":2273134,"uid":84044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"一早睇穿你龍野啦"},{"pid":"b90d2e5aefafed529c7f2475eb403356b125f3c5","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"最硬淨竟然係梁家榮"},{"pid":"97d4f9165dc093f74d5c6533a9bbb4152529911d","tid":2273134,"uid":95577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b90d2e5aefafed529c7f2475eb403356b125f3c5","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"最硬淨竟然係梁家榮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"鑊鑊都係姓馮果個政務官做刀手"},{"pid":"ad8e4d8745664015bc62dc742722ed52359c1e80","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d4f9165dc093f74d5c6533a9bbb4152529911d","tid":2273134,"uid":95577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b90d2e5aefafed529c7f2475eb403356b125f3c5","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"最硬淨竟然係梁家榮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"鑊鑊都係姓馮果個政務官做刀手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"撚屌AO"},{"pid":"abb44b00e577b8347dad54ee6928b671793a2693","tid":2273134,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"因為工作而被捕<br />\n屌你啦Management"},{"pid":"8d513c92043bccd9e102d3f7fad5c261babe65e7","tid":2273134,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb44b00e577b8347dad54ee6928b671793a2693","tid":2273134,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"因為工作而被捕<br />\n屌你啦Management"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:19:09.000Z","msg":"外判連責任外判"}]}